name: Hot Toys #013 Mbak Kunti
description: She is well known in Indonesia. A woman ghost with long hair and she also has many names. Some people named her "Mbak Kunti", "Kuntilanak', "Pontianak", "Puntianak" or "Sundel Bolong". Folk says she dies in childbirth and the child had not yet been born. So, she wandered around haunted people in search of her baby.
